
 - install virtualbox (https://www.virtualbox.org/)
 - gem install vagrant
 - cd setup
 - vagrant box add ubuntu1110 http://timhuegdon.com/vagrant-boxes/ubuntu-11.10.box
 - vagrant up
 - vagrant ssh
   % cd pdf
   % sh -x ./test.sh

 (from the host machine, not inside the VM):

 - open pdf/screenshot.pdf
 
To shut down the VM:
 - vagrant halt
